# Frontend Konvansiyonları

## Yapı

```
frontend/src/
  app/           # shell agent — router, layout, providers
  api/           # shell agent — fetch client, types
  auth/          # shell agent — login, register
  features/
    houses/      # frontend-houses agent
    expenses/    # frontend-expenses agent
    dashboard/   # frontend-dashboard agent
```

## API

- Base URL: `import.meta.env.VITE_API_URL`
- Access token memory; refresh httpOnly cookie (backend template ile uyumlu)
- Hata gösterimi: `ApiErrorBody` from `@housemate/shared`

## UI

- Feature agent'lar `features/<name>/` altında sayfa + bileşen
- Ortak layout: `app/AppLayout.tsx` — feature agent düzenlemez
- Türkçe UI metinleri (PRD hedef kitle)

## State

- Ev bağlamı: `HouseProvider` (shell) — aktif `houseId`
- Server state: fetch + basit cache; gereksiz Redux yok
